title: Maldives Foreign Exchange Reserves
description: Foreign Exchange Reserves in Maldives decreased to 531.80 USD Million in September from 649.30 USD Million in August of 2022. Foreign Exchange Reserves in Maldives averaged 740.44 USD Million from 2015 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 978.70 USD Million in September of 2021 and a record low of 456.50 USD Million in December of 2016. This page provides - Maldives Foreign Exchange Reserves- actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Maldives Monetary Authority
